data.description: Gorgeous, brand new corner lot home... Move in ready! 100% complete! Awesome floor plan. 3 bedrooms/ 2.5 baths. Great room style has island kitchen with quartz counters and LVP flooring. French doors to den/office on main level. Large loft for extra living space. Big and bright laundry room. All electric with heat pump for efficient heating and cooling. Large fenced backyard with landscaping. Beautiful new neighborhood that is conveniently located in the heart of Vancouver!
